    <bf:note>
      <bf:Note>
	<rdfs:label>A thin piece of wood painted black and white with a wooden symbol spray-painted in black and gold affixed to one side and a handwritten poem with the title "22, 23" by Michel Butor on the other side.</rdfs:label>
      </bf:Note>
